{"tid":2488613,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[町田啓太x赤楚衛二] 如果30歲還是處男，似乎就能成為魔法師 /演員相關討論  57","createTime":"2021-04-14T10:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T00:58:36.000Z","uid":5000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"81e6ea8670b74757163d791f9190e9d5d18cb809","tid":2488613,"uid":5000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4R9fAsOLpfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4R9fAsOLpfI&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=b45a1e26\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4R9fAsOLpfI</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://realsound.jp/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/20200904-cherimaho-main.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frealsound.jp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F20200904-cherimaho-main.jpeg&h=a8a9ec7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豐田悠在pixiv連載中的作品「如果30歲還是處男，似乎就能成為魔法師」真人日劇化；故事講述由於安達（赤楚衛二飾演）30歲了還保有處男之身，因此變得能使用魔法。他得到的是「只要接觸就能讀取人心」這般多餘又樸素的魔法之力。<br />\n這樣的某日，他無意間讀取到工作優秀的同期帥哥同事──黑澤（町田啟太飾演）的心，黑澤的心中，充滿了對安達的無限愛戀!?<br />\n赤楚衛二x町田啟太主演BL漫改電視劇《如果30歲還是處男，似乎就能成為魔法師》，東京電視台10月8日開播<br />\n<br />\n官方twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tx_cherimaho?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftx_cherimaho%3Fs%3D21&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=a77641e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tx_cherimaho?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n町田啓太ig<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/keita_machida_official?igshid=z29dmx3q10b1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fkeita_machida_official%3Figshid%3Dz29dmx3q10b1&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=cca2a004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/keita_machida_official?igshid=z29dmx3q10b1</a><br />\n<br />\n赤楚衛二ig<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/akasoeiji?igshid=etjx3bl1d64v\" data-sr-ur